<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>AIR CONDITIONING - HEATER SYSTEM: 2000, 4000, AND 8000 - 12/06/1994 and After - REMOVE AND INSTALL - BLOWER
        MOTOR AND LOW/HIGH PRESSURE SWITCH RELAYS
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="remove" graphiccount="1">
        <title>BLOWER MOTOR AND LOW/HIGH PRESSURE SWITCH RELAYS</title>
        <svcprocinfo>
            <para>The blower motor and low/high pressure switch relays are located on the passenger side, behind the
                lower right instrument panel cover (
                <hotlnk xrefid="f1601622">Figure 22</hotlnk>).
            </para>
            <figure id="f1601622" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="g1601622" filename="../figg16/G1601622.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="248px"
                         scalefitheight="272px"/>
                <caption>Figure 22. Blower Motor and Low/High Pressure Switch Relays</caption>
            </figure>
        </svcprocinfo>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Remove</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Remove the right lower instrument panel cover. Refer to
                    <hotlnk document="s16016_HL1601607.xml" xrefid="hl1601607">LOWER RIGHT INSTRUMENT PANEL, HEATER-A/C
                        ASSEMBLY COVER AND DRAIN TRAY
                    </hotlnk>
                    . This will expose the relays.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Service the relay(s) that require replacement.</para>
            </step1>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Install</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Turn the key switch to ON and check the operation of the relay(s). After this operation
                    check, turn the key switch OFF.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Install the lower right instrument panel cover. Refer to
                    <hotlnk document="s16016_HL1601607.xml" xrefid="hl1601607">LOWER RIGHT INSTRUMENT PANEL, HEATER-A/C
                        ASSEMBLY COVER AND DRAIN TRAY</hotlnk>.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcsubproc>
    </svcproc>
